♦ Follow up and track the progress of client cases;

Client Experience Enhancement & Reporting
♦ Review client feedback and propose necessary changes to enhance client satisfaction;
♦ Achieve KPIs for sales revenue, the number of contracts, number of solution consulting meetings, and report periodically.

Other details will be further discussed in the interview.

